long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Proxy Management App

With the Thordata proxy extension, you can easily manage proxy settings in Chrome. Easily turn proxies on or off and seamlessly work with any proxy provider, supporting fast switching of residential, ISP and datacenter proxies.

With the Thordata extension, you can hide your real location and access geo-restricted content. All traffic will be forwarded through a secure intermediate proxy server, ensuring that the target website only sees our clean IP address, not your real IP.

Say goodbye to tedious proxy configuration, Thordata allows you to do everything in just a few clicks!

Features and Benefits:
- Compatible with any proxy service provider
- Easily switch between different types of proxies
- Quick setup, get started in seconds
- Simplified configuration, user-friendly interface
- Free to use, no additional fees

How to set up Chrome proxy extension?

✔Download and add to browser
✔Add proxy profile
✔Secure connection and anonymous browsing
